text: Kokemäki is a town in south-west Finland. The city has a population of 7,653 (30 June 2015) and an area of 531,27 km². Through Kokemäki flows the Kokemäenjoki river which is 121 km long. ==Other websites== *Kokemäki website Category:Cities in Finland Category:Municipalities of Satakunta
title: Kokemäki
